<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B1306026002" page = "2">
<title>
MAF Sensor Inspection
</title>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Remove MAF and IAT sensor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B1306025"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Connect MAF and IAT sensor (1) to 12 V battery (2), 3 new 1.5 V batteries in series (3) and voltmeter (4) as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Check that voltage varies depending on blowing air as shown in graph below.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If faulty condition is found, replace MAF and IAT sensor. 
